# UIButtonSystem  (sbx)

## Purpose
Toggles the demo UI panel's visibility. Returns early until SandboxConfigSingletonComponent is
present. When the toggle button is released (a UIOnReleaseOneFrameComponent whose element id matches
the toggle button), it finds the panel by UUID and emits a UIUpdateEnableOneFrameComponent flipping
the panel's current enabled flag. Acting on release rather than press debounces the interaction to
one toggle per click.

## Input Components
| Component | Access | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| SandboxConfigSingletonComponent | read | Toggle button and panel ids; guard |
| UIOnReleaseOneFrameComponent | read | Release on the toggle button triggers the toggle |
| BaseComponent | read | Locates the panel by UUID and reads its current enabled flag |

## Output Components
| Component | Access | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| UIUpdateEnableOneFrameComponent | add (oneframe) | Emitted on the panel to flip its enabled flag |
